WEBVTT

00:07:00.346 --> 00:07:03.919
And in that advice was,
"Do not talk to the street kids,

00:07:05.038 --> 00:07:07.469
at no point leave your baggage unattended

00:07:08.889 --> 00:07:11.330
and in all counts, do not go swimming."

00:07:11.354 --> 00:07:13.125
(Laughter)

00:07:13.149 --> 00:07:15.910
So I was like, "I don't know
if this is a good idea."

00:07:16.904 --> 00:07:19.260
Serge has got his arm around me.

00:07:19.284 --> 00:07:21.011
I'm like, "OK." So there I am.

00:07:21.035 --> 00:07:22.045
(Laughter)

00:07:22.069 --> 00:07:25.641
I literally handed all my cameras,
all my equipment, to these street kids.

00:07:25.665 --> 00:07:27.474
And they took it.

00:07:27.498 --> 00:07:30.241
It's kind of funny to know,
if you look in the background,